name: .handmade cream floral purse.
description:
.handmade cream floral purse.

Purse outer material is 100% cotton print fabric from Japan.
Acrylic Felt in between fabrics for shape.
Lining is also 100% cotton.
15cm Metal purse frame with clasp clip.
 
Approximate Measurements:
: Height: 13 cm
: Length from middle: 17cm
 
 - Items will be shipped within 2 business days from Sydney Australia once payment has been confirmed. -
 
Thank you for looking!
